data.description: Instant equity! Listed at almost $20k under recent appraised value. Updates galore! Take a look at the documents to see a complete list of all the updates done to this home! This is not your average manufactured home. In the heart of the home you'll find a completely re-done kitchen w/ all new cabinetry, butcher block counter tops, and an entire pantry wall. The primary bedroom has a roomy walk-in closet, the en suite bath has a tiled shower and tons of storage. The three additional bedrooms each have a walk-in closet. The family room features a custom built wall unit and two big, beautiful window showcasing the backyard. The home sits at the front of the lot giving you a huge backyard oasis. Enjoy your outdoor space on the back deck, which has new railings installed over the summerGreat opportunity to own a home on almost a half acre in a neighborhood (NO HOA, DD2 schools!)  $1100 credit available towards buyer's closing costs with preferred lender.
